# ─── Go ───────────────────────────────────────────────
# Compiled binaries. `go build` drops an executable named after the
# module ("war") right here; we never commit build output — anyone can
# rebuild it from source with `go build`.
/war
*.exe
*.test          # binaries produced by `go test -c`
*.out           # coverage/profile output (e.g. coverage.out)

# `go test` and the race detector working files
*.prof

# ─── Editors / IDEs ──────────────────────────────────────
# GoLand / IntelliJ project settings — machine-specific, not source.
.idea/

# VS Code (in case you switch editors mid-project)
.vscode/

# ─── macOS ────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
